{"tid":43152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[救命]點解廿歲就有靜脈曲張","createTime":"2016-12-17T09:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T17:00:54.000Z","uid":55483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a116c13f65e0198378e37f8f2a3d21780e2ac16","tid":43152,"uid":55483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"隻小腿有條蛇型物體腫起左，都幾大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗可以講下"},{"pid":"9aef505da8d1ec517b68746dcc7b5176aa69e431","tid":43152,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:56:22.000Z","msg":"中醫學上，靜脈曲張屬「脈痹」、「筋瘤」範圍。症型可再細分為濕熱下注、血瘀氣滯、肝腎不足及氣血虛弱四大類。治療以活血、清熱利濕、化瘀行氣為主。患者更應減少進食辛辣食品，以及菠菜、蒜葱等溫血熱氣食物，以免加劇瘀血阻礙<br />\n<br />\n維基咁寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64104a1db09a67bb4406955f547a2ccac2ac923d","tid":43152,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"去買彈性繃帶著"},{"pid":"686cded0e9558d77e3e06d3ac751c0fed27b5d08","tid":43152,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T10:22:33.000Z","msg":"都叫你唔好成日著高跟鞋架啦男人老狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47b760e9f6181fb768ece9c0d7ea8483c246ea1","tid":43152,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"我諗得做手術先可以好番"}]}